      <note>Join: used to combine two or more streams (data already in the pipeline).
it can change the number of the rows in the data steeam (eitther increase or decrease).
</note>
      <width>538</width>
    </notepad>
    <notepad>
      <backgroundcolorblue>210</backgroundcolorblue>
